Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:53.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have lived for all these years... without ever making a decision. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:57.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,This... is my penance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:01.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was unable to become an Eternal Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nor was I able to go to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I remained here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to touch another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:13.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to be held by another. Yet still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why did your body have to become like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I refused to choose a sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was chosen to become the keeper of the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you wouldn't choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:32.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that future maidens would not err the way I have erred.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,To continue to stand here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:39.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is my punishment for continuing to run from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:03:00.48,Titles,,0,0,0,,Choices
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:05.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is to be formally disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, we have decided that you must now go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:09.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why must we also give up our standing as sibyllae?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:18.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of your duties will be taken over by priestesses from the Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:19.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:26.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're not even allowed to be Simoun sibyllae anymore? So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't stay here on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well... forcing them to make such a choice all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can they be expected to decide so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,They need to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are asking only for a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:47.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Compared to the long history of the Simulacrum Theocracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,it is but a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:00.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,You heard about what happened to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:01.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:03.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:06.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be leaving the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Holy Land has no desire to fly the Simoun any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:19.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,To demonstrate the fact, our entire maintenance crew is being relocated to the Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wherever we end up, it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:28.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun are the holy chariots of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I try to get close...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:35.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. The truth is that I've realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the Simoun any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:43.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy as long as you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can understand if you despise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've gotten smaller, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:56.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:06.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become a man and tinker with the Simoun with you, but... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you going to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:30.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:34.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess you always wanted to be a man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:38.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bet you don't even care that they're forcing us to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:42.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're always—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:43.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm scared too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's scary becoming an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want someone to help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:54.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to be protected! But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forget it, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're such a dummy, Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:07.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy... dummy... dummy... dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fighting with your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, you guys are so childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:22.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still kids. It's too early for you to become adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:27.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Vyura, everyone in Rubor already chose their sex, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:30.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ones who were going to inherit a family business became men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest... well, you know, it depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:34.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about you, Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:39.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me? Whatever. I don't really care which sex I end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:42.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure I wouldn't be saying that if I had a lover, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? But everyone told me that you liked Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I keep telling them that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,But... I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It feels kinda lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what... becoming an adult is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:09.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see... so becoming an adult is a lonely thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez, that's why I told you not to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're always such a drag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're a dummy, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:31.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling a dummy? Dodo-legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:32.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:36.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine! Go back on your own then, loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:39.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Du-Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Du... mmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:47.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're a dummy, Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even when we quarrelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,she couldn't even think of words to insult me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:01.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,So all she ever said was "dummy."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:07.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you know, she just never gave up, and kept tagging along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:11.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seriously... what a dummy I have for a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:15.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder when Alti...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,...stopped being such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be the one to protect you, Nee-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,She got this determined look in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:29.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Her arms and legs grew longer, and it was almost like... she became more of an adult than me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lots of things were happening all the time, so I didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That Alti...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she's still the same old idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I kept looking the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,But... even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,She'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are things that you can still do,\Neven if you're no longer a sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such as forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,To forgive a fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and to be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:05.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think we can still be sibyllae even after we choose our sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really {\i1}do{\i0} like you, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,My feelings won't change whether I become a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I'll never stop respecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:32.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've heard that the High Priestess has left the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:37.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, don't bother answering. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:46.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I can tell you this. There's no way I'll do it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:51.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Going to another world just 'cause you wanna see Amuria again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:54.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's all you care about! So I can't do a Ri Maajon with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:02.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did Onashia show me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:07.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never to be held by another. Yet still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remain here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:15.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia... will she have to stand there forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:18.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to be forgiven by anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:23.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:28.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought that perhaps I should take some of Mamiina's belongings with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh. Her suitcase is under her bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,When I return home, Mamiina's mother will be there, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that I could give these to her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,It still smells like Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:50.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope this will comfort her mother, even if only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:55.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we even... save anyone anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think it will be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,We struggle so much just to save ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:08.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But... perhaps if we try really, really hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...maybe we can save at least one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,One... person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:13.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, do you have somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,That one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun... disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:26.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard that the Highland soldiers are looking for her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:32.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe she didn't wanna become an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:35.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. Yun, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,She must have found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:38.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:39.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whatever. She's so standoffish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just leaving like that, without even saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:49.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah... but once Chor Tempest is disbanded, we're all gonna go our separate ways anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:57.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is something that I need to tell you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,About another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:26.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's crazy! To think the Emerald Ri Maajon did that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:30.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it will save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:37.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soon, we will all choose our sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our lives here on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:45.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,But those two... they won't choose a sex, and they'll stay the way they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not choose their sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and stay the way they are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,When we all become adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:57.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,and the feelings that we have now fade away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,in some other time, those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:06.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,will stand in the shining lands, looking just as they do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:14.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So those two will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:14.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if we all become adults...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...they'll remain as they are now, forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The eternal now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:29.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, you don't have to go to the other world. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what we decide, we should at least tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That we've not going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't need to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to know what happened to Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:13:59.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:06.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love you, who strive for life in spite of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:10.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love you, who saved me from the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of going to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:17.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if I'm with you, I think—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:18.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:24.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn't want... to hear your feelings... about liking me and stuff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't need to give me an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:26.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just thought that I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was so sudden! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:00.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one I love... is you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:52.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to save the wandering spirits of my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was the thought that kept me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,But... I always knew the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,That the dead can no longer be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:13.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. I realized that there's one soul that only I can save. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had secretly hoped...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that you would say those words to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:32.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Long ago, I decided not to choose a sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:37.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, my heart was unable to stay a maiden's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:41.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now... I am trying to run away, once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:45.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,while pushing all my responsibilities onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:46.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:24.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are... beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It sounds very lively out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,That voice... that has to be Sibylla Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uwaa! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, were you ever planning to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:24.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's our last day on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait! Alti!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nah, don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The view is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's dance, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:53.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, let the {\i1}Messis{\i0} carry you to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:51.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to ride on a helical motor train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:57.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,May I ask what has happened to Sibylla Neviril and Sibylla Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:20:01.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,They said that they wished for a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:03.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:05.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:12.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,After I'm an adult, I'll come visit again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,The mountains are getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,It should be lunchtime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:58.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh! I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I asked for some snacks before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is anyone hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those look yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:08.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:09.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want the veggie one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Rodore?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll have meat, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me, too, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Boy, am I hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mmm, delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:22.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is Rodore's, and here you go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:22.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:24.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Man, if you had sandwiches, you should've told us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:39.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:41.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
